MADONNA / LIKE A VIRGIN (AARON DARC REMIX)

mp3 320kbps

Madonna’s iconic dance groove gets re-interpreted, using the original studio vocal, as an electro-ballad. A cult hit and a must have for any Madge fan! Like you’e heard it for the very first time…
I've also uploaded the Aaron Darc remix of Fergie / Fergalicious :)
